thread.title: Julie H.
thread.title_full: Mabel's Labels reviewed by Julie H.

author: Julie H.
title: Julie H.
text:
A great selection, great service, quick turn around time and so easy to use the web site for ordering personal labels for my Children and as gifts for friends and family. The quality of the labels are awesome, the kids usually out grow the clothing or item before the label needs to be replaced.
Thank you Mabel's for great Labels!
